fields.title: 部署hill1895时踩过的坑
fields.content:
首先贴上源码地址：https://github.com/hill1895/hill1895

克隆到本地后，根据requirement.txt安装依赖包，其中mysql采用python2版本，因为3.X版本安装mysql时会报configparse错误，stackoverflow上有人说可以用six包import，尝试未果。

修改setting.py中的mysql配置项，并创建项目数据库，create database时需要指定默认的编码方式（CREATE DATABASE tinyCMS DEFAULT CHARACTER SET gbk COLLATE gbk_chinese_ci;），否则会在添加blog等步骤时产生1366-incorrect-string-value-error，具体的解决方案：https://www.cnblogs.com/moinmoin/archive/2012/01/18/1955419.html

利用django内置的makemigrations和migrate命令初始化所有表(如果遇到表不存在的问题，可以先删除migration目录下的部分迁移文件重新建表)；利用createsuperuser创建后台管理员账号；

runserver开启服务器

依次添加标题1、标题2、tags等的具体信息

fields.title: opencv调用摄像头拍照或者录视频
fields.content:
参考文献：https://docs.opencv.org/3.0-beta/doc/py_tutorials/py_gui/py_video_display/py_video_display.html


have a try   

import numpy as np
import cv2
 
cap = cv2.VideoCapture(0)
 
# Define the codec and create VideoWriter object
fourcc = cv2.VideoWriter_fourcc(*'XVID')
out = cv2.VideoWriter('output.avi',fourcc, 20.0, (640,480))
 
while(cap.isOpened()):
    ret, frame = cap.read()
    if ret==True:
        frame = cv2.flip(frame,0)
 
        # write the flipped frame
        out.write(frame)
 
        cv2.imshow('frame',frame)

        #cv2.imwrite('demo.jpg',frame)

        if cv2.waitKey(1) & 0xFF == ord('q'):
            break
    else:
        break
 
# Release everything if job is finished
cap.release()
out.release()
cv2.destroyAllWindows()

fields.title: 录音amr文件转换为mp3
fields.content:
原博客地址:http://blog.csdn.net/pj_developer/article/details/72778792


import os   
import subprocess   
   
def amr2mp3(amr_path,mp3_path=None):   
    path, name = os.path.split(amr_path)   
    if name.split('.')[-1]!='amr':   
        print 'not a amr file'   
        return 0   
    if mp3_path is None or mp3_path.split('.')[-1]!='mp3':   
        mp3_path = os.path.join(path, name.split('.')[0] +'.mp3')   
    error = subprocess.call(['ffmpeg','-i',amr_path,mp3_path])   
    print error   
    if error:   
        return 0   
    print 'success'   
    return mp3_path   
   
if __name__ == '__main__':   
    amr_path = 'demo.amr'   
    amr2mp3(amr_path)

fields.title: 算法小栗子-最长不重复字符串
fields.content:
# Given a string, find the length of the longest substring without repeating characters.
#
# Examples:
#
# Given "abcabcbb", the answer is "abc", which the length is 3.
#
# Given "bbbbb", the answer is "b", with the length of 1.
#
# Given "pwwkew", the answer is "wke", with the length of 3. Note that the answer must be a substring, "pwke" is a subsequence and not a substring.
#

# 核心思想是抓住开头的index,每次遇到重复的字母出现,就需要修改开头index为该重复字母的index+1

class Solution(object):
    def lengthOfLongestSubstring(self, s):
        """
        :type s: str
        :rtype: int
        """
        start = maxstr = 0
        usedic = {}
        for i in range(len(s)):
            if s[i] in usedic and start<=usedic[s[i]]:
                start = usedic[s[i]]+1
            else:
                maxstr = max(maxstr,i-start+1)
            usedic[s[i]]=i
        return maxstr


s = Solution()
print(s.lengthOfLongestSubstring("umvejcuuk"))

fields.title: 算法小栗子-最长镜像字符串
fields.content:
Given a string

Given a string s, find the longest palindromic substring in s. You may assume that the maximum length of s is 1000.

Example:

Input: "babad"Output: "bab"Note: "aba" is also a valid answer.

 

Example:

Input: "cbbd"Output: "bb"



def longestpalindrome(self, s):
   n = len(s)
   maxp = ''
   span = 0
   for i in range(n):
       for j in range(i,i+2):
           k = i
           m = j
           while k>=0 and m < n and s[k]==s[m]:
               k -= 1
               m += 1
           l = m -k-1
           if l>span:
               span = l
               maxp = s[k+1:m]
   return maxp

fields.title: 算法小栗子-股票何时出售
fields.content:
Say you have an array for which the ith element is the price of a given stock on day i.

If you were only permitted to complete at most one transaction (ie, buy one and sell one share of the stock), design an algorithm to find the maximum profit.

Example 1:

Input: [7, 1, 5, 3, 6, 4]
Output: 5

max. difference = 6-1 = 5 (not 7-1 = 6, as selling price needs to be larger than buying price)

Example 2:

Input: [7, 6, 4, 3, 1]
Output: 0

In this case, no transaction is done, i.e. max profit = 0.


class Solution(object):
    def maxProfit(self, prices):
        """
        :type prices: List[int]
        :rtype: int
        """
        maxp = 0
        leng = len(prices)
        minv = float('inf')
        for i in range(leng):
            minv = min(minv,prices[i])
            if prices[i]-minv>maxp:
                maxp = prices[i]-minv
        return maxp

fields.title: nginx+ngrok将本地主机反向代理到自己的域名
fields.content:
1.安装ngrok

mkdir ngrok #创建名称为ngrok的目录

apt-get update #更新包管理器

apt-get install git  #安装git

git clone https://github.com/inconshreveable/ngrok.git

2.安装go

apt-get install golang

3.设置环境变量

export NGROK_DOMAIN="xxxx.cn"  #设置环境变量，xxx.cn为你的域名

4.生成ngrok用的证书

cd ngrok
openssl genrsa -out rootCA.key 2048openssl req -x509 -new -nodes -key rootCA.key -subj "/CN=$NGROK_DOMAIN" -days 5000 -out rootCA.pem
openssl genrsa -out server.key 2048openssl req -new -key server.key -subj "/CN=$NGROK_DOMAIN" -out server.csr
openssl x509 -req -in server.csr -CA rootCA.pem -CAkey rootCA.key -CAcreateserial -out server.crt -days 5000

5.拷贝证书到tls

cp rootCA.pem assets/client/tls/ngrokroot.crt  #复制rootCA.pem到assets/client/tls/并更名为ngrokroot.crt
cp server.crt assets/server/tls/snakeoil.crt #复制server.crt到assets/server/tls/并更名为snakeoil.crt

cp server.key assets/server/tls/snakeoil.key #复制server.key到assets/server/tls/并更名为snakeoil.key

6.编译成可执行文件

#win服务端GOOS=windows GOARCH=386 make release-server

#win客户端GOOS=windows GOARCH=386 make release-client

#linux服务端GOOS=linux GOARCH=386 make release-server

#linux客户端GOOS=linux GOARCH=386 make release-client

7.配置服务器端:公共服务器

cd pathtongrok

./bin/ngrokd -tlsKey="assets/server/tls/snakeoil.key" -tlsCrt="assets/server/tls/snakeoil.crt" -domain="***.cn"  -httpAddr=":8081" -httpsAddr=":8082" -tunnelAddr=":8083"

8.配置客户端:本地主机

拷贝生成的ngrok,创建ngrok.cfg,内容如下

server_addr: "***.cn:8083"

trust_host_root_certs: falsetunnels:

 http:
   subdomain: "www"
   proto:
     http: "8090"
     
 https:
   subdomain: "www"
   proto:
     https: "8091"

 ssh:
   remote_port: 2222
   proto:

     tcp: "22"

9.开启ngrok client

./ngrok -config ngrok.cfg start http https ssh


此时可以通过https://www.***.cn:8082和http://www.***.cn:8081访问到本地主机的8091和8090端口


以下为nginx配置

打开conf/nginx.conf,修改

   server {
       listen       80;
       server_name  127.0.0.1:8080;
       location / {
           proxy_pass   http://127.0.0.1:8080;
       }

   }

即可将80端口转发到8080端口

重启：nginx -s reload

fields.title: canvas画图异常的解决方法
fields.content:
参考：http://www.cnblogs.com/foreverZ/p/7365271.html

绘制小程序分享二维码时用到了canvas，ctx.drawImage(url, spoint,epoint,width,height)，然而两张image总是加载出一张本地的，服务器端的图片压根没有发出请求，最终解决方法如下：

wx.downloadFile({

  url: url,

  success: function (res) {

    ctx.drawImage(res.tempFilePath, 0, 0, 300, 500);

    ctx.draw();

  }

})

先将服务器端的图片请求到本地，再传给drawimage函数。
